Here's a PlantUML component diagram focusing on the security aspects of the Qubes OS CTAP Proxy architecture:

```plantuml
@startuml marmarek_qubes-app-u2f

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<secure>> LightGreen
  BorderColor<<secure>> DarkGreen
}

package "Browser VM" {
  [Browser] as browser
  [CTAPHID Emulation] as hidemu <<secure>>
  [Qrexec Client] as qrexec_client <<secure>>
}

package "sys-usb VM" {
  [Qrexec Server] as qrexec_server <<secure>>
  [CTAP Protocol Handler] as ctap_handler <<secure>>
  [USB Stack] as usb_stack
}

cloud "Qrexec" as qrexec <<secure>>

[CTAP Token] as token

browser --> hidemu : CTAP requests
hidemu --> qrexec_client : Forward requests
qrexec_client --> qrexec : Secure IPC
qrexec --> qrexec_server : Secure IPC
qrexec_server --> ctap_handler : Forward requests
ctap_handler --> usb_stack : Communicate with USB device
usb_stack --> token : Physical USB connection

rectangle "Security Measures" {
  [Policy Enforcement] as policy <<secure>>
  [VM Isolation] as isolation <<secure>>
}

policy -[hidden]-> isolation
policy .[#red]left.> qrexec : Controls access
isolation .[#red]left.> "Browser VM" : Isolates browser
isolation .[#red]right.> "sys-usb VM" : Isolates USB stack

@enduml
```